{"tid":23743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"洪欣囝囝兩度改名 張鎬濂跟後父闖娛圈","createTime":"2016-12-05T06:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T10:25:33.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dee688208822d58443a2dd1c97917cfb9ff34d2","tid":23743,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"洪欣同莫少聰多年前愛得轟烈，洪欣仲未婚生咗囝囝莫鎬廉，近年洪欣改嫁張丹峰，囝囝索性跟後父姓，改名張浩鋒。最近浩鋒同後父張丹峰拍住上，拍內地嘅電視劇《致青春》，做張丹峰嘅童年版，好有camera face㗎。 <br />\n<br />\n浩鋒入行，開通微博同粉絲聯繫，生父莫少聰見有渠道同個仔聯絡，即時私信搵仔，雖然浩鋒微博俾面後父繼續用張姓，但個名用番「鎬濂」，原來洪欣個仔個名最初係用三點水嗰個「濂」㗎，唔通兩仔爺重修關係？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jH28zQh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjH28zQh.jpg&h=012d5a04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc4c1d94c22b53a32a76691b1f620fb87df82d0c","tid":23743,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686154be53b26e9c4da22ca0413123ee347f215a","tid":23743,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"我真係要恭喜你呀.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d206fd50161cfd64ba9df755b55ff1f188dfbf44","tid":23743,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4867630b52b4807bf7c516344609d8a58a95e20e","tid":23743,"uid":9382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"成街人都睇死你個仔改名跟後父發曬明星夢呀，咁多窿路架，唔想講野啦我地。"},{"pid":"2a5fd9741fc93596b4655dc2a32c66532d1814a7","tid":23743,"uid":9382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"我又對邊個好呀而家我呀<br />\n你對邊個好？你對鎬濂唔好咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/06/182527_ad1052f41918ec6e40275013653c5aae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F182527_ad1052f41918ec6e40275013653c5aae.jpg&h=0b77e668&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}